CatDescriptText: Cutline of images published in the Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 13, 1954, pg. 12 reads: " More Queen Contestants - Another group of Pittsburgh teen-agers who are clamoring to wear the crown of Hill City Queen includes, left to right,...Carol Calcutta...Barbara Winters...Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Two frames: Portrait of Carol Calcutta wearing plaid short sleeved collared shirt, posed in front of light colored background in Harris Studio for Hill City Teen Queen contest; Portrait of Barbara Winters wearing light colored short puff sleeved blouse with floral embroidery on sheer yoke, posed in front of light colored background in Harris Studio for Hill City Teen Queen contest
